ni-ai.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/technology/personaltech/google-gemini-ai.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss</guid><atom:link rel="standout" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/technology/personaltech/google-gemini-ai.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss" /><description>Despite its early stumbles, Google’s Gemini has leapfrogged ChatGPT in relevance and usefulness. Soon, it will be ubiquitous.</description><dc:creator>Brian X. Chen</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 17:45:06 GMT</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Artificial intelligence</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Computers and the Internet</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Tech Industry</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">ChatGPT</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Online advertising</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Anthropic</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Google</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">OpenAI</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Gary Rivlin</category><media:content url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2026/05/19/business/19techfix/19techfix-videoSixteenByNineJumbo1600.jpg" medium="image"><media:credit>Sisi Yu</media:credit></media:content></item><item><title>Bipartisan Bill Would Impose New Annual Fee on Electric Vehicles</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/business/energy-environment/electrc-vehicles-annual-fee-congress.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/business/energy-environment/electrc-vehicles-annual-fee-congress.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss</guid><atom:link r